SEARCH
Package com.org.Traini8.Service

Interface TrainingCenterRetreiveService

All Known Implementing Classes:
TrainingCentreRetreiveServiceImpl
public interface TrainingCenterRetreiveService
The TrainingCenterRetrieveService interface defines the operations that can be performed to retrieve information about training centers. This service interface is used to abstract the retrieval of training center data, providing various methods to fetch training centers based on different criteria.

  • Method Details

    • findAllTrainingCenters

      List<TrainingCentre> findAllTrainingCenters()
      Retrieves all training centers available in the database.
      Returns:
      a list of TrainingCentre representing all training centers. If no training centers are found, this method returns an empty list.

    • findByMultipleCriteria

      List<TrainingCentre> findByMultipleCriteria(String centerCode, String centerName, Integer minCapacity, Integer maxCapacity, String contactEmail, String contactPhone, String city, String state, String pincode, List<String> courses)
      Retrieves a list of training centers based on multiple search criteria. Any parameter can be null, in which case it will not be used as a filter.
      Parameters:
      centerCode - Optional filter by center code.
      centerName - Optional filter by center name.
      minCapacity - Optional filter for minimum capacity of the center.
      maxCapacity - Optional filter for maximum capacity of the center.
      contactEmail - Optional filter by contact email address.
      contactPhone - Optional filter by contact phone number.
      city - Optional filter by city where the center is located.
      state - Optional filter by state where the center is located.
      pincode - Optional filter by postal code.
      courses - Optional list of courses; centers must offer all listed courses if specified.
      Returns:
      a list of TrainingCentre that match the specified criteria. If no centers meet the criteria, this method returns an empty list.
